5. **Recording** — countdown to "Go," then recording starts. If `hints_enabled` is true, a lightweight live-hints layer runs client-side (see Phase 6) and surfaces at most one small, non-blocking hint at a time. Recording behaves exactly as today otherwise.
6. **Upload → async processing → feedback** — unchanged. Deep content analysis (structure, argument quality, relevance) stays exclusively in the existing post-session LLM pipeline; live hints never attempt this.

